title: (x) Reeds Brook - Garth Graphic {Mark S}
content: Looks like [Garth Graphic Black](http://web.archive.org/web/20050516142042/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/agfa/garth-graphic/black/testdrive.html?s=REEDSBROOK&p=48) with some horizontal scaling to make it more condensed. The shading--or even the whole thing--may have been hand-painted by the looks of it.
author: Mark Simonson
